== English ==
=== Etymology ===
A [[euphemistic]] replacement of "[[God]]" in [[for God's sake]].
=== Interjection ===
'''[[for]] [[goodness]]' [[sake]]'''
# {{idiom}} {{euphemism}} This interjection expresses [[frustration]], [[exasperation]], [[annoyance]]
#: '''''For goodness' sake''', get off the [[computer]]! You've been on there for ages!''
# {{idiom}} {{euphemism}} This interjection expresses [[surprise]] or [[amazement]]
#: '''''For goodness' sake''', I spelt that word correctly. I never knew I could do that''
